column5: I just wanted to take a minute to wish all here a Very merry Christmas! Many of you I have met and I hope to meet many more of you fine folks real soon! Hold your famlies real tight and may God bless every one of you all!
Hyyvaa Joulua to you and yours as well. May the good Lord keep you all near, dear, and well over the Christmas season.
Merry Christmas and all the best for 2013 !
Merry Christmas to all.  Hope u have a happy, healthy holiday!
Best wishes and happy holidays to everyone!!!!!!!!!!!!.
Merry Christmas to all, and to all a good night.  Don't you dare think about drinking and driving!
Merry Christmas, everyone!  Here's a Christmas song, it's a few years old now, but maybe next year we'll do a new one.  http://rivironline.com/files/rivir-whatchildisthisorganicmix.mp3
